      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.mu0emKq7UEsMFpWt]{Spell Sergeant}</p>\n<p>The ability to change your position, even across short distances, can bring victory from sure defeat. After you make a successful melee attack, you can teleport up to 10 feet. This movement does not provoke an @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.GtSmojwt4d6rdEkm#attack-of-opportunity]{attack of opportunity}. Once you’ve used flash flourish, you can’t do so again until after you take a 10-minute rest to recover Stamina Points, though you can spend 1 Resolve Point to recharge the ability immediately.</p>"
